hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Looking for a job quantum heart max God forbid I ever walk in a store and a salesman tries to sale me a new PC. I'd take Windows 8 under only one condition. Free and allow me to smash the damn thing in the store while recording for a Youtube video. That would be my first ever video posted to Youtube. Hell, I'd have so much fun recording that video, cleaning up the mess would be quite pleasant. Normally I wouldn't be so destructive, but Windows 8 brings out the Taz in me.
